main event: Two circular objects were sighted in Topeka, Kansas, on April 16-21, 1967.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 10 minutes., The objects were observed through a ground visual observation., The conclusion noted a possibility of the objects being airships., There was an indication of physical evidence present., This report is part of the Project Blue Book, a U.S. Air Force program for investigating UFOs.
sighted object: two circular objects in the sky
